&lt;h2 id=&#34;Windows&#34;&gt;&lt;a href=&#34;#Windows&#34; class=&#34;headerlink&#34; title=&#34;Windows&#34;&gt;&lt;/a&gt;Windows&lt;/h2&gt;&lt;p&gt;For Windows 10, Windows 8, Windows 7, and Windows Vista systems that use User Account Control (UAC).&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ol&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Run Notepad as Administrator.&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;  Press the &amp;#x201C;Windows&amp;#x201D; key, type in &amp;#x201C;Notepad&amp;#x201D;.&lt;/li&gt;
