&lt;h2 id=&#34;1-Using-Last-Known-Good-Configuration&#34;&gt;&lt;a href=&#34;#1-Using-Last-Known-Good-Configuration&#34; class=&#34;headerlink&#34; title=&#34;1. Using Last Known Good Configuration&#34;&gt;&lt;/a&gt;1. Using Last Known Good Configuration&lt;/h2&gt;&lt;p&gt;This method will replace the corrupt Windows configuration and restore the &amp;#x201C;Last Known Good Configuration&amp;#x201D;.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
