&lt;li&gt;  Press and hold the F8 key as your computer restarts. You need to press F8 before the Windows logo appears. If the Windows logo appears, you&amp;#x2019;ll need to try again by shutting down and restarting your computer.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;  On the Advanced Boot Options screen, use the arrow keys to highlight Last Known Good Configuration (advanced), and then press Enter.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;  Windows will then resume starting normally.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;h2 id=&#34;2-Using-System-Restore&#34;&gt;&lt;a href=&#34;#2-Using-System-Restore&#34; class=&#34;headerlink&#34; title=&#34;2. Using System Restore&#34;&gt;&lt;/a&gt;2. Using System Restore&lt;/h2&gt;&lt;ul&gt;
